            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Herculi <lb n="2"/>Saxsano <note>sic</note> <lb n="3"/><expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Mettius <lb n="4"/>Seneca |(centurio) <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> XV et <lb n="6"/>vexsillarii <note>sic</note> <lb n="7"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> eiusdem <lb n="8"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olverunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 6: kleines S zwischen X und I; wohl nachträglich eingefügt. Z. 6 (Ende): vom letzten Buchstaben noch der untere Teil erhalten. (B): CIL 13, 07700; ILS 3455; Matijević: Z. 6: VEXILLARI.</p>
            </div>
